                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>On January 11, Mr. Dulles met with members of the House Committee on Foreign
                    Affairs to discuss with them a Japanese peace settlement and the proposal for a
                    Pacific Ocean Defense Council. Mr. Allison’s memorandum of this meeting is
                    printed on page 790.</p>
            </div>
